{"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:","symbolKind":"method","title":"setEmails:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings. Each must be a valid email format."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"emails"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Associates multiple email addresses with the current device for omnichannel","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"email campaigns. This is useful when users have multiple email addresses"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(work, personal, etc.) and want to receive communications on all of them.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All provided emails will be linked to the same device and user ID,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"enabling unified targeting across all addresses.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register multiple emails from user profile:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func syncEmailsFromProfile(_ profile: UserProfile) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primary = profile.primaryEmail {","            emails.append(primary)","        }","        if let secondary = profile.secondaryEmail {","            emails.append(secondary)","        }","        if let work = profile.workEmail {","            emails.append(work)","        }","","        guard !emails.isEmpty else { return }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails)","","        \/\/ Update tags with email count","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"email_count\": emails.count,","            \"has_work_email\": profile.workEmail != nil,","            \"has_multiple_emails\": emails.count > 1","        ])","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user."}],"title":"setEmails:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"}}}